courses.customDesc: One course from each of the following GE areas must be completed: A1, A2, A3, B1, B2, B3, (B4 [lab] must be completed with either B2 or B3), B1-B5 elective, C1, C2, C3, C4, D1, D3, D5, and F. C4, D5, and F should be taken only after Junior standing is reached (90 units). One (1) course must be completed from B1, in addition to STAT 217. No SOC class may be taken to fulfill GE D5. Refer to online catalog for GE course selection and Graduation Writing Requirement (GWR).
